{"id": "1241149966861209600", "channel_id": "1241149966861209600", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "```他的聲名遠播，他的家財萬貫，這是百年以來他對世人救濟的輝煌成果。當你身陷水火之中，只需高呼他的名字，以最卑微的姿態向他求助，慈悲為懷的大善人威爾斯會不吝代價地救你於苦難中。\n你只需要負責感激涕零，銘記他的功勞，讚頌他的美德。即使是這麼微小的報答，彌薩格大學也未曾向他求取任何資助，或許永遠不會。```\n\n這是沒錢委託只好再次使用AI繪圖的野貓，三位一體終於出完了<:NekoBday:1200338373555011615> \n定位類似於魔術師，不過威爾斯偏向於把棄牌堆當成另一個超維空間跟垃圾場，把不想看到的牌跟一定要看到的牌都塞進棄牌堆放著，並控制牌堆使其無法重製。\n\nP1預告圖來自網路上的AI圖\nP2&P3的部分風味文字來自於[克蘇魯公社](https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv23849063/) 的原創文章\nP3命輪圖來自[Firsik](https://www.shutterstock.com/zh/image-vector/poster-two-color-versions-byakhee-starsteed-2001220049) 的作品\n\n>>>前作：\n⁠https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1229156600737042483\nhttps://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1240360398876573787", "timestamp": "2024-05-17T22:06:51.551000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-17T22:07:12.264000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "nekocash", "emoji_id": "1200338280932200459", "count": 5}], "attachments": [{"id": "1241149967348007024", "filename": "557366b860541cfc.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 21717, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1241149966861209600/1241149967348007024/557366b860541cfc.jpg?ex=69cb9cbb&is=69ca4b3b&hm=2dd03eb29154381642e18651f0e9f02fc9ac7143ec0a4fce2a88412d7f696f2b&"}, {"id": "1241149967683424317", "filename": "742d0dbb0967a385.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 139552, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1241149966861209600/1241149967683424317/742d0dbb0967a385.jpg?ex=69cb9cbb&is=69ca4b3b&hm=9c2aa670f4faea278f1566e6323f4a24fd567bc0468003ae34c094828c2578fd&"}, {"id": "1241149968153055333", "filename": "149d8ad0e2454dec.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 149291, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1241149966861209600/1241149968153055333/149d8ad0e2454dec.jpg?ex=69cb9cbb&is=69ca4b3b&hm=f7ca31dfb5742c78889a936c241a3f48903abac20009366